metadata.name: Bridge to Paradise
metadata.description: Each sunrise holds its own magic, but there are those that leave you awestruck like no other. This photograph captures one such extraordinary moment.  Over the course of the past couple of years, I revisited this spot several times, driven by a vision in mind of a certain image I wanted to capture. Unfortunately, unforeseen weather conditions and timing stopped me from my original aspirations. However, on the final morning available to shoot, the sky burst forth in a symphony of colors beyond my wildest dreams.
